Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷 现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,四点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷 现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,四点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要先让自己笑起来啊
